	/w gm &{template:DnD35StdRoll} {{spellflag=true}} {{name=@{character_name}}} {{subtags=casts [Dispel Evil](https://dndtools.net/spells/players-handbook-v35--6/dispel-evil--2312/) }} {{School:= Abjuration  [Good]}} {{Level:= **Good 5**, Paladin 4, VassalofBahamut 4, KnightoftheChalice 4, Cleric 5, Elysium 5, Cloistered Cleric 5}} {{Components:= V, S, DF}} {{Range:= Touch}} {{Target:=You and a touched evil creature from another plane; or you and an enchantment or evil spell on a touched creature or object}} {{Duration:=1 round/level or until discharged, whichever comes first}} {{Savingthrow:=See text }} {{Save DC:=[[@{spelldc5}+@{sf-Abjuration}]]}} {{Spellresistance:=No }}  {{compcheck=Concentration: [[ {1d20+ [[ @{concentration} ]] }>[[?{Damage Taken|0}+15+0]] ]] }} {{succeedcheck=Success! @{subjective} casts @{possessive} spell!}} {{failcheck=@{subjective} fails @{possessive} concentration :( }} {{notes=Shimmering, white, holy energy surrounds you.
